  • Classes in de.uni_kl.cs.discodnc.network used by de.uni_kl.cs.discodnc.experiments 
    Class Description
    Network
    Servers in a network object correspond to buffers that may be shared by different flows, i.e., a network corresponds to the server graph of a (physical) network.
